	<li><strong>Examinations </strong>
	<ul>
		<li><strong>​</strong><em>Qualifying Examination:</em> Not required.</li>
		<li><em>Preliminary (Research) Examination:</em> Required; oral.</li>
	</ul>
	</li>
	<li><strong>Dissertation</strong> Required.</li>
	<li><strong>Other Requirements</strong> Each student must present a seminar based on his or her research in <span class="sc_courseinline"><a href="/search/?P=CHE%20595" title="CHE 595" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'CHE 595');">CHE 595</a></span> at least once.</li>

</ul>

<h3>Entering with MS in Chemical Engineering</h3>
<ul>
	<li><strong>Minimum Semester Hours Required</strong> 76 from the MS. 32 semester hours are given for the MS.</li>
	<li><strong>Course Work </strong></li>
</ul>
